- Finally, a brand new user interface for a better experience!
- New Music Area, now you can choose your preferred "P4P" music.
- Added PLANS, now you can start a long-term plan to archive your goals!
- Added new workouts, each Monday you will get an entirely new and free workout!
- New 3D virtual trainer for many exercises, we will update rest of the exercise library very soon.
- Check the update and discover all the news yourself.

If you like this update, please leave a good review for us - will be much appreciated ;-) Otherwise, please avoid writing bad reviews and just send us a feedback by mail, we will work hard to improve our App in the next update!
